I'm using the webclient and i push "start server" and it says "Successfully created"

any idea whats wrong?

item.title: Why Can't I Play Moparscape?
item.dc:creator: @s4nta s4nta
item.description:
@s4nta wrote:

Well, first off you’re not meant to press start server, you’re meant to press other button. Then go to file<new I.P<add the I.P if it has port click file<port<add in port… then create a random name of your choice and password, and login. remember, If you’re going into a server that has hamachi, download hamachi at www.hamachi.cc and conenct to it, then join an existing server type in I.P and pass, then go to webclient and join.
